race.description: Sapphire Hair By Bentleys Maiden Plate
race.comment: LADY YARROW (10) nine-start Maiden expected to get off the mark in this average contest. Stalked the speed from the low draw when going under narrowly for a solid second over 1500m at Kembla Grange in a Super Maiden. Has a fitness edge over the bulk of these and should be able to get cover from the sticky draw. ROSE DIAMOND (12) returned without a trial when a game on-pace second over 1200m at Nowra. Placed at this trip and shapes as one of the better hopes. ALAMAGAN (6) went back from the awkward gate on resumption when a plugging ninth over 1300m at Kembla Grange. Maps well and can run into the minor money. ARGANTORATI (8) chipped away late from the wide gate when respectable sixth over 1180m at Gundagai in a Super Maiden. Looking for this trip now and can race closer from the inside barrier.
